{"chapter_number":90,"bismillah_pre":true,"revelation_order":35,"revelation_place":"makkah","name_arabic":"البلد","name_complex":"Al-Balad","name_simple":"Al-Balad","verses_count":20,"pages":[594,594],"meaning":{"text":"The City","en":"The City","id":"Negeri"},"verses":[[[1,6024,"90:1","لَا أُقْسِمُ بِهَٰذَا الْبَلَدِ",["Nay! I swear by this city.","Aku bersumpah dengan negeri ini (Mekah),"],594,30,60,238,null,null],[2,6025,"90:2","وَأَنتَ حِلٌّ بِهَٰذَا الْبَلَدِ",["And you shall be made free from obligation in this city--","dan engkau (Muhammad), bertempat di negeri (Mekah) ini,"],594,30,60,238,null,null],[3,6026,"90:3","وَوَالِدٍ وَمَا وَلَدَ",["And the begetter and whom he begot.","dan demi (pertalian) bapak dan anaknya."],594,30,60,238,null,null],[4,6027,"90:4","لَقَدْ خَلَقْنَا الْإِنسَانَ فِي كَبَدٍ",["Certainly We have created man to be in distress.","Sungguh, Kami telah menciptakan manusia berada dalam susah payah."],594,30,60,238,null,null],[5,6028,"90:5","أَيَحْسَبُ أَن لَّن يَقْدِرَ عَلَيْهِ أَحَدٌ",["Does he think that no one has power over him?","Apakah dia (manusia) itu mengira bahwa tidak ada sesuatu pun yang berkuasa atasnya?"],594,30,60,238,null,null],[6,6029,"90:6","يَقُولُ أَهْلَكْتُ مَالًا لُّبَدًا",["He shall say: I have wasted much wealth.","Dia mengatakan, “Aku telah menghabiskan harta yang banyak.”"],594,30,60,238,null,null],[7,6030,"90:7","أَيَحْسَبُ أَن لَّمْ يَرَهُ أَحَدٌ",["Does he think that no one sees him?","Apakah dia mengira bahwa tidak ada sesuatu pun yang melihatnya?"],594,30,60,238,null,null],[8,6031,"90:8","أَلَمْ نَجْعَل لَّهُ عَيْنَيْنِ",["Have We not given him two eyes,","Bukankah Kami telah menjadikan untuknya sepasang mata,"],594,30,60,238,null,null],[9,6032,"90:9","وَلِسَانًا وَشَفَتَيْنِ",["And a tongue and two lips,","dan lidah dan sepasang bibir?"],594,30,60,238,null,null],[10,6033,"90:10","وَهَدَيْنَاهُ النَّجْدَيْنِ",["And pointed out to him the two conspicuous ways?","Dan Kami telah menunjukkan kepadanya dua jalan (kebajikan dan kejahatan),"],594,30,60,238,null,null],[11,6034,"90:11","فَلَا اقْتَحَمَ الْعَقَبَةَ",["But he would not attempt the uphill road,","tetapi dia tidak menempuh jalan yang mendaki dan sukar?"],594,30,60,238,null,null],[12,6035,"90:12","وَمَا أَدْرَاكَ مَا الْعَقَبَةُ",["And what will make you comprehend what the uphill road is?","Dan tahukah kamu apakah jalan yang mendaki dan sukar itu?"],594,30,60,238,null,null],[13,6036,"90:13","فَكُّ رَقَبَةٍ",["(It is) the setting free of a slave,","(yaitu) melepaskan perbudakan (hamba sahaya),"],594,30,60,238,null,null],[14,6037,"90:14","أَوْ إِطْعَامٌ فِي يَوْمٍ ذِي مَسْغَبَةٍ",["Or the giving of food in a day of hunger","atau memberi makan pada hari terjadi kelaparan,"],594,30,60,238,null,null],[15,6038,"90:15","يَتِيمًا ذَا مَقْرَبَةٍ",["To an orphan, having relationship,","(kepada) anak yatim yang ada hubungan kerabat,"],594,30,60,238,null,null],[16,6039,"90:16","أَوْ مِسْكِينًا ذَا مَتْرَبَةٍ",["Or to the poor man lying in the dust.","atau orang miskin yang sangat fakir."],594,30,60,238,null,null],[17,6040,"90:17","ثُمَّ كَانَ مِنَ الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا وَتَوَاصَوْا بِالصَّبْرِ وَتَوَاصَوْا بِالْمَرْحَمَةِ",["Then he is of those who believe and charge one another to show patience, and charge one another to show compassion.","Kemudian dia termasuk orang-orang yang beriman dan saling berpesan untuk bersabar dan saling berpesan untuk berkasih sayang."],594,30,60,238,null,null],[18,6041,"90:18","أُولَٰئِكَ أَصْحَابُ الْمَيْمَنَةِ",["These are the people of the right hand.","Mereka (orang-orang yang beriman dan saling berpesan itu) adalah golongan kanan."],594,30,60,238,null,null],[19,6042,"90:19","وَالَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا بِآيَاتِنَا هُمْ أَصْحَابُ الْمَشْأَمَةِ",["And (as for) those who disbelieve in our communications, they are the people of the left hand.","Dan orang-orang yang kafir kepada ayat-ayat Kami, mereka itu adalah golongan kiri."],594,30,60,238,null,null],[20,6043,"90:20","عَلَيْهِمْ نَارٌ مُّؤْصَدَةٌ",["On them